1
00:00:13,307 --> 00:00:15,117
Design For Living. Yvonne speaking.
家居设计公司，我是Yvonne.

2
00:00:16,548 --> 00:00:18,399
Bill Collins! How are you?
Bill Collins! 你好吗?

3
00:00:19,696 --> 00:00:20,846
Fine. Great.
Fine. Great.

4
00:00:21,872 --> 00:00:22,969
We're very busy working.
我们的工作非常忙，

5
00:00:23,769 --> 00:00:25,503
But we always have time for you.
不过对你我们总是有时间的.

6
00:00:27,911 --> 00:00:29,489
You're buying a house?
你要买房子了?

7
00:00:33,567 --> 00:00:37,484
Fabulous. Of course we're interested.
太棒了. 我们当然感兴趣.

8
00:00:39,273 --> 00:00:45,646
Why don't you stop by next Wednesday.
你何不下星期三过来坐一会儿?

9
00:00:47,371 --> 00:00:52,168
Two o'clock? Terrific. See you then.
两点钟? 好极了. 到时候见.

10
00:00:56,305 --> 00:00:58,370
-What? -We can't do it.
-What? -这活儿我们不能接.

11
00:00:58,671 --> 00:01:00,340
We can't not do it.
我们不能不接这个活儿.

12
00:01:01,362 --> 00:01:04,978
Yvonne. Work is good. Killing ourselves is bad.
Yvonne. 有活儿干当然好. 苦了我们自己可就不好了.

13
00:01:06,127 --> 00:01:08,635
Turning away clients is bad.
把上门的客户回绝掉才不好.

14
00:01:09,245 --> 00:01:11,261
We like Bill. This is good news.
我们都喜欢Bill，这可是好消息.

15
00:01:12,047 --> 00:01:17,423
Yes. We like Bill. I also like eating and sleeping.
Yes. 我们是喜欢Bill. 可是我也喜欢吃, 喜欢睡.

16
00:01:17,755 --> 00:01:20,886
And it's very pleasant every once in a while to take a vacation.
如果还能时不时地度度假的话，那就太美了.

17
00:01:21,671 --> 00:01:24,081
What are you? afraid of success?
你怎么啦? 害怕成功吗?

18
00:01:25,441 --> 00:01:25,707
Oh please.
Oh please.

19
00:01:31,564 --> 00:01:33,309
It's no use complaining, is it?
抱怨是没有用的，不是吗?

20
00:01:33,739 --> 00:01:35,952
Nope. You'll thank me later.
Nope.你以后会感谢我的.

21
00:01:38,045 --> 00:01:40,816
I know. That's what kills me.
我知道. 那才是让我痛苦的事.

